    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上古守护 是一款第三人称动作角色扮演游戏，融合了 PvP 和 PvE 元素，并拥有独特的奇幻职业。你可以独自或与朋友一起冒险，寻找宝藏，提升等级，并击败任何阻碍你前进的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344320/extras/fb51d68ec3bb3204bf488bee335b2435.poster.avif?t=1771353329\" width=1170 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344320/extras/fb51d68ec3bb3204bf488bee335b2435.webm?t=1771353329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344320/extras/fb51d68ec3bb3204bf488bee335b2435.mp4?t=1771353329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以从六个经典的奇幻职业中进行选择并升级：战士、游侠、猎人、牧师、法师和圣骑士，每个职业都有自己独特的角色模型、盔甲、武器和技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344320/extras/75ed9c5437cca945a44499d31ab6a5e7.poster.avif?t=1771353329\" width=1170 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344320/extras/75ed9c5437cca945a44499d31ab6a5e7.webm?t=1771353329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344320/extras/75ed9c5437cca945a44499d31ab6a5e7.mp4?t=1771353329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索五个独特区域和多达32种不同的生物。你可以独自一人或与最多两名队友一起，参与PvE探险、PvPvE撤离模式或快节奏的竞技场模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344320/extras/b7615c47c48e35c266c7783bad7fd65f.poster.avif?t=1771353329\" width=1170 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344320/extras/b7615c47c48e35c266c7783bad7fd65f.webm?t=1771353329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344320/extras/b7615c47c48e35c266c7783bad7fd65f.mp4?t=1771353329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险都要带上你最好的装备和药水，但要小心。死亡是有代价的，在PvPvE模式中，其他人可能会夺走你的战利品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344320/extras/d15ca7c9c3d289d5ab69db2d2d82ecad.poster.avif?t=1771353329\" width=1170 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344320/extras/d15ca7c9c3d289d5ab69db2d2d82ecad.webm?t=1771353329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344320/extras/d15ca7c9c3d289d5ab69db2d2d82ecad.mp4?t=1771353329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你找不到想要的战利品，可以使用<strong>上古守护</strong>丰富的制作和升级系统来制作它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在石港镇的商人那里积累声望，即可解锁新的制作配方。建造你的小屋，解锁各种设施，例如用于加工矿石的熔炉、用于获得休息经验值的床，以及可以饲养金甲虫并从中获取金线以获得被动收入的小动物栖息地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级六个独特的职业，每个职业都拥有强大的技能、武器和装备套装，以及强大而独特的被动技能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以单人游玩，也可以与最多两名好友组队进行合作冒险。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索并征服五张不同的地图，每张地图都充满了挑战、宝藏和等待你发现的秘密。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从<strong>金色溪流</strong>农场开始，踏上PvE远征之旅，追捕残暴的莫索格，这个威胁着<strong>上古守护</strong>人民的恶魔。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战PvPvE夺宝模式，风险越大，回报越高——如果不幸阵亡，你的战利品将被幸存者夺走。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入<strong>竞技场</strong>，体验快节奏、考验技巧的玩家对战——无需担心装备损失，只是荣誉之战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>石港镇与五位关键商人建立声望</strong>，解锁专属装备、制作配方和稀有材料。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>建造并装饰你的个人小屋</strong>，配备熔炉、织布机、制革厂、小动物栖息地和炼金装置等功能性建筑，提升你的制作能力和游戏进程。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成<strong>17条战役任务线</strong>，揭开上古守护的传说，并获得强大的宝藏奖励。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接受任务板上超过110个轮换任务，任务每日和每周更新，带来无穷无尽的挑战和奖励。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验赛季重置</strong>，进度将被清零，同时迎来全新内容、更新和改变世界的事件——每个赛季，所有玩家都将从零开始。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一个生动的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上古守护 未来计划推出大量新内容。以下是一些值得期待的亮点：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新职业: 女巫</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新史诗区域：卡斯</p></li></ul>",
